            <title>[LU-8922] deactive MDT might cause 2 dir stripes created in the same MDT.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8922</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Deactive one MDT might cause 2 stripes created in the same MDT. I will cook a patch.&lt;/p&gt;

